{
    "publish_date": "2012-09-13T17:37:56.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT14M20S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "SUROOSH ALVI: And this is about\nas quiet as it gets.", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "18.14"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hajj is the largest annual\npilgrimage in the world.", 
            "dur": "2.726", 
            "start": "26.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It happens in Mecca,\nSaudi Arabia.", 
            "dur": "2.529", 
            "start": "29.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And for Muslims, it&#39;s a\nrequirement that you have to", 
            "dur": "2.015", 
            "start": "31.725"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "do once in your lifetime.", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "33.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Saudi government estimated\nthat last year there were over", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "35.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "3 million pilgrims who attended,\nbut the unofficial", 
            "dur": "2.78", 
            "start": "38.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "number is much higher.", 
            "dur": "3.31", 
            "start": "41.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My parents are originally\nfrom Lahore, Pakistan.", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "44.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They&#39;re practicing Muslims, and\nlast year they decided it", 
            "dur": "3.51", 
            "start": "47.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was time for them\nto perform Hajj.", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "50.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I went with them to help them\nwith their journey, but", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "52.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "also for myself as well.", 
            "dur": "2.04", 
            "start": "55.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was the first time\nfor all of us.", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "57.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I didn&#39;t go thinking I\nwas going to make a VBS", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "59.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "documentary.", 
            "dur": "0.77", 
            "start": "61.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I just took the smallest\nhandicam we had the office and", 
            "dur": "3.38", 
            "start": "62.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "literally shot from the hip.", 
            "dur": "1.402", 
            "start": "65.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re not allowed to shoot in\nmost of the holy places.", 
            "dur": "2.098", 
            "start": "67.002"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this is the footage I\nmanaged to sneak out.", 
            "dur": "4.15", 
            "start": "69.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We flew on Saudi Arabian\nairlines.", 
            "dur": "1.725", 
            "start": "73.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was about a 10 hour flight\nfrom JFK to Medina, where we", 
            "dur": "3.565", 
            "start": "74.975"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "spent 6 days getting mentally\nprepared for the Hajj that we", 
            "dur": "3.345", 
            "start": "78.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "were about to embark on.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "81.885"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In pre-Islamic times, Medina\nwas a place where the", 
            "dur": "3.32", 
            "start": "85.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "travelers who were crossing the\ndesert in camel caravans", 
            "dur": "4.11", 
            "start": "89.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would come to rest.", 
            "dur": "0.92", 
            "start": "93.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was kind of like\na desert oasis.", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "94.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In modern times it&#39;s kind of the\nsame thing, but there are", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "96.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "less camels and more shopping\nmalls and hotels.", 
            "dur": "3.015", 
            "start": "98.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s also stunning mosque\nthere called the Prophet&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.475", 
            "start": "101.945"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Mosque, which is the\nsecond-holiest site in Islam.", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "104.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you&#39;re there, you basically\njust go to the", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "112.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "mosque five times a day, for six\ndays straight, to get into", 
            "dur": "3.91", 
            "start": "113.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a meditative state.", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "117.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The mosque is huge.", 
            "dur": "0.95", 
            "start": "120.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It holds almost 700,000\npeople.", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "121.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when we were there for\nthe Friday prayer, it", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "123.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was pretty much full.", 
            "dur": "1.276", 
            "start": "125.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Flying to Mecca from Medina\nwas really interesting.", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "130.99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Before we went to the airport,\nwe cleansed ourselves in a", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "133.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "very specific way.", 
            "dur": "1.34", 
            "start": "136.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then we had to put on a\nwhite seamless garment made", 
            "dur": "4.22", 
            "start": "137.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "our of terrycloth that all the\npilgrims have to wear.", 
            "dur": "2.64", 
            "start": "142.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s a renunciation of the\nlife that you come from and is", 
            "dur": "4.42", 
            "start": "144.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "supposed to put everyone\non the same level.", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "149.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There is no upper class\nor lower class.", 
            "dur": "1.83", 
            "start": "152.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Everyone&#39;s the same.", 
            "dur": "0.75", 
            "start": "153.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s just you and the sheet,\nand that&#39;s it.", 
            "dur": "3.248", 
            "start": "154.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[PRAYING]", 
            "dur": "3.422", 
            "start": "157.868"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is called getting into\na state of Irham.", 
            "dur": "2.24", 
            "start": "161.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Besides the clothes, there\nare a lot of other rules.", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "163.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can&#39;t smoke.", 
            "dur": "0.475", 
            "start": "166.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can&#39;t have sex.", 
            "dur": "1.175", 
            "start": "166.995"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can&#39;t shave.", 
            "dur": "1.21", 
            "start": "168.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can&#39;t cut your nails,\nand there are a", 
            "dur": "3.209", 
            "start": "169.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bunch of other no-no&#39;s.", 
            "dur": "2.801", 
            "start": "172.589"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we got this charter, just\nfor the pilgrims, and 10", 
            "dur": "3.56", 
            "start": "175.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "minutes after the plane took off\nfrom Medina, the captain", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "178.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "announced that we&#39;d flown over\na designation, and we were in", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "181.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the zone near Mecca.", 
            "dur": "1.67", 
            "start": "184.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we all had to start\nsaying a prayer.", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "186.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And our group guide got onto the\nloudspeaker system of the", 
            "dur": "3.67", 
            "start": "188.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "airplane and started\nyelling the prayer.", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "192.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Everyone started chanting it.", 
            "dur": "1.695", 
            "start": "195.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I had a moment where I\nlooked around and saw all of", 
            "dur": "3.205", 
            "start": "196.705"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "these men and women in their\nwhite robes, the men with", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "199.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "their beards, and just thought,\nif someone from the", 
            "dur": "1.76", 
            "start": "202.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "West could see us right now,\nthey would think we were a", 
            "dur": "1.73", 
            "start": "204.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bunch of fanatical Jihadis\non some kind of an insane", 
            "dur": "3.25", 
            "start": "206.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "mission, when in reality, it was\njust pilgrims excited to", 
            "dur": "3.474", 
            "start": "209.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "go on this spiritual quest.", 
            "dur": "1.306", 
            "start": "213.024"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I think what was most odd about\nthis flight were the", 
            "dur": "3.19", 
            "start": "217.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "flight attendants, who were all\nFilipino, wearing their", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "220.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "normal Saudi flight attendant\noutfits, looking like they", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "224.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would rather have any\nother gig in the", 
            "dur": "1.37", 
            "start": "227.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "world than this one.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "228.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We landed in Jeddah and\ntook a bus into Mecca.", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "234.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that ride into the city was\none of the wilder scenes", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "236.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve ever seen in my life.", 
            "dur": "1.41", 
            "start": "239.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There were all these pilgrims\ncoming from all directions in", 
            "dur": "3.5", 
            "start": "241.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all kinds of vehicles.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "244.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you see them riding\non the tops of cars,", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "246.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and vans, and buses.", 
            "dur": "1.322", 
            "start": "248.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I remember seeing a pilgrim\njumping from the roof of one", 
            "dur": "2.918", 
            "start": "250.212"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bus to another.", 
            "dur": "1.17", 
            "start": "253.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Everybody&#39;s just trying\nto get to the city.", 
            "dur": "2.146", 
            "start": "254.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Mecca is not a very big city.", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "268.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And during the year, it&#39;s a\nrelatively mellow place,", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "270.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "except during the\nweek of Hajj.", 
            "dur": "1.59", 
            "start": "273.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The city completely transforms\nand half the challenge of", 
            "dur": "3.37", 
            "start": "274.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "completing your Hajj is getting\nall these rituals done", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "278.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in a very strict timeline,\ndealing with the fact there", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "281.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "are about three million other\npeople there who try to do the", 
            "dur": "2.23", 
            "start": "283.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "exact same thing at\nthe same time.", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "286.03"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After we checked into our\nhotel in Mecca we walked", 
            "dur": "3.44", 
            "start": "291.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "towards the Grand Mosque,\nwhich is also", 
            "dur": "1.77", 
            "start": "294.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "known as Masjid Al-Haram.", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "296.66"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s the holiest\nplace in Islam.", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "298.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s a massive structure.", 
            "dur": "2.04", 
            "start": "300.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This Moscow can hold upwards\nof four million people with", 
            "dur": "2.89", 
            "start": "302.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "its outdoor and indoor space,\nwhich, during Hajj, is", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "305.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "technically the largest\ngathering of people in the", 
            "dur": "3.43", 
            "start": "308.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "world at any given time.", 
            "dur": "1.89", 
            "start": "312.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This mosque is what Muslims\npray towards from", 
            "dur": "1.853", 
            "start": "313.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all over the world.", 
            "dur": "1.867", 
            "start": "315.783"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as you&#39;re walking towards\nit, you feel the", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "317.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "anticipation build.", 
            "dur": "1.01", 
            "start": "319.76"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "People have been waiting\ntheir whole lives to", 
            "dur": "2.36", 
            "start": "320.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "come to this place.", 
            "dur": "1.37", 
            "start": "323.13"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And once you enter the mosque,\nthen you see the Kabeh.", 
            "dur": "4.485", 
            "start": "324.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Kabeh is a black\nbox in the center", 
            "dur": "2.46", 
            "start": "332.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of the Grand Mosque.", 
            "dur": "1.61", 
            "start": "334.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it was built\naround 2000 BC.", 
            "dur": "2.96", 
            "start": "336.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And people have been praying\ntowards it since", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "339.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "before Islam started.", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "341.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when Prophet Muhammad\nfinally showed up, he cleaned", 
            "dur": "3.09", 
            "start": "343.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "up the place, got rid of all the\nidols that the pagans had", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "346.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "been worshipping, and reordained\nthe building as the", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "348.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "House of God.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "351.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So in the Grand Mosque, we had\nto do our first ritual, which", 
            "dur": "3.15", 
            "start": "358.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is called the Tawaf, which\nis basically doing seven", 
            "dur": "3.83", 
            "start": "361.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "counterclockwise laps\naround the Kabeh.", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "365.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s kind of like being in\na mosh pit with hundreds of", 
            "dur": "4.61", 
            "start": "368.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "thousands of people, but instead\nof it being full of", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "373"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "angry young punk kids, we were\nup against aggressive", 
            "dur": "4.67", 
            "start": "376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Bangladeshi grandmothers.", 
            "dur": "1.89", 
            "start": "380.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I had my parents on each arm\ninterlocked, and we held each", 
            "dur": "3.98", 
            "start": "382.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "other as we went around the\nstructure seven times.", 
            "dur": "2.465", 
            "start": "386.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You&#39;re staring at the Kabeh.", 
            "dur": "1.51", 
            "start": "394.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a very intense\nand heavy vibe.", 
            "dur": "3.07", 
            "start": "396.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the one thing that&#39;s a total\nbummer is you look up", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "399.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and all you see are these\nmassive, luxury five-star", 
            "dur": "4.09", 
            "start": "401.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hotels for the super-rich\nMuslims who want to pray from", 
            "dur": "3.325", 
            "start": "406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the confines of their room.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "409.325"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After running around the Kabeh\nseven times you have to do a", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "427.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bunch of other rituals in order\nto complete your Hajj.", 
            "dur": "2.045", 
            "start": "430"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have five days\nto get it done.", 
            "dur": "1.125", 
            "start": "432.045"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s kind of like being\non a scavenger hunt.", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "433.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have a checklist.", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "435.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to be smart.", 
            "dur": "1.02", 
            "start": "436.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you have to use strategy in\norder to make this happen", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "437.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on schedule.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "440.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to do the Sa&#39;i, which\nis walking and running back", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "444.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and forth between two hills.", 
            "dur": "2.55", 
            "start": "448.03"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Back in the day he used to be\noutdoors and now it&#39;s been", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "450.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "turned into indoor structure\nwith two", 
            "dur": "2.8", 
            "start": "453.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "very, very long corridors.", 
            "dur": "1.565", 
            "start": "456.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You have to spend a day\nat Mount Arafat.", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "463.03"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s where the Prophet\ndelivered", 
            "dur": "1.05", 
            "start": "465.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "his last sermon from.", 
            "dur": "1.48", 
            "start": "466.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you spend the day in prayer,\nand contemplation, and", 
            "dur": "3.17", 
            "start": "468.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "beg for forgiveness for\nall of your sins.", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "471.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a very important day,\nand, after spending the", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "474.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "majority of it in a tent, I\nwalked out and went in the", 
            "dur": "3.79", 
            "start": "476.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "direction of the mountain.", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "480.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I walked through this wild\nscene with people everywhere", 
            "dur": "4.37", 
            "start": "481.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "camped out with their animals.", 
            "dur": "1.877", 
            "start": "486.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as I got closer to mount\nArafat, it was such an", 
            "dur": "3.7", 
            "start": "493.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "incredible sight because\nit had been completely", 
            "dur": "1.68", 
            "start": "496.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "transformed.", 
            "dur": "0.7", 
            "start": "498.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It looked like a snow-covered\npeak.", 
            "dur": "1.29", 
            "start": "499.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Our tour group operators, before\nwe went on this trip,", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "508.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "gave us some guidelines.", 
            "dur": "1.209", 
            "start": "511.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the last point on the\nsheet said, be patient.", 
            "dur": "3.63", 
            "start": "512.299"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Be very patient.", 
            "dur": "1.61", 
            "start": "515.929"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Be very, very patient.", 
            "dur": "2.401", 
            "start": "517.539"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I fully grasped the meaning of\nthis when we had to take a", 
            "dur": "2.77", 
            "start": "519.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "three-kilometer bus ride,\nand it ended up", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "522.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "taking eight hours.", 
            "dur": "1.35", 
            "start": "525.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was the middle of the night,\nand we had to collect", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "526.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "stones, it was one of our\nrituals, in a place called", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "529.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[INAUDIBLE].", 
            "dur": "0.79", 
            "start": "531.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And so we got off the bus.", 
            "dur": "1.715", 
            "start": "532.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We navigated our way around\nsleeping bodies all over the", 
            "dur": "3.065", 
            "start": "534.085"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ground, found the stones.", 
            "dur": "2.18", 
            "start": "537.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then it was time to pray,\nand so we just threw the", 
            "dur": "4.5", 
            "start": "539.33"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "prayer rugs down on\nthe side of the", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "543.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "highway and hit the mats.", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "545.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "After picking up the stones,\nwe got back on the bus and", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "576.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "drove to Mina.", 
            "dur": "1.036", 
            "start": "579.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The Valley of Mina is where\nthe majority of", 
            "dur": "1.794", 
            "start": "580.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the pilgrims stay.", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "582.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a tent city that fills\nup with, essentially, the", 
            "dur": "3.01", 
            "start": "583.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "population of Seattle for a\nweek and then, after Hajj", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "586.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ends, it clears out again\nand goes away.", 
            "dur": "2.895", 
            "start": "589.17"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s tents as far as\nthe eye can see.", 
            "dur": "3.041", 
            "start": "592.065"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[SINGING IN PRAYER]", 
            "dur": "6.974", 
            "start": "595.106"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "From [INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "0.55", 
            "start": "602.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "we arrived in Mina, and that&#39;s\nwhere we had to stone Satan.", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "602.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s the next ritual.", 
            "dur": "0.966", 
            "start": "606.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And this one was actually\na lot of fun.", 
            "dur": "2.204", 
            "start": "607.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You had to throw 21 stones,\nseven at three separate", 
            "dur": "4.2", 
            "start": "609.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Satan-stoning stations.", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "613.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I finally got to see\nwhat Satan looks like.", 
            "dur": "2.19", 
            "start": "615.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Up until a couple years ago,\nSatan looked like three big", 
            "dur": "3", 
            "start": "618.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pillars sticking out\nof a large pit.", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "621.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the space wasn&#39;t big\nenough, and there was a", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "623.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "stampede and people died.", 
            "dur": "1.12", 
            "start": "625.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the Saudi government, they\nbuilt three ramps the size of", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "626.35"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a multi-lane highway, and\nthere were three pillars", 
            "dur": "3.04", 
            "start": "629.46"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "inside of it that represent\nthe devil.", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "632.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They&#39;re lit in shades\nof green.", 
            "dur": "2.19", 
            "start": "634.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there&#39;s a strange rumbling\nloud sound coming out of them.", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "636.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as my dad pointed out, the\nwhole thing made Satan look", 
            "dur": "2.81", 
            "start": "640.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "quite surreal.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "643.01"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Before we finished the Hajj, we\nhad to repeat some of the", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "646.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "rituals that we&#39;d\nalready done.", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "649.77"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we had to revisit Satan,\nthrow rocks at", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "651.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "him two more times.", 
            "dur": "1.63", 
            "start": "653.49"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We had to go back to back to\nMecca from Mina and do another", 
            "dur": "3.44", 
            "start": "655.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "seven counterclockwise laps.", 
            "dur": "2.51", 
            "start": "658.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then it was time for Eid,\nwhich marks the official end", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "661.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of Hajj, which is a\nbig celebration.", 
            "dur": "2.62", 
            "start": "663.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s the end of the state of\nIrham that we&#39;ve been in.", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "666.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we slaughter an animal\nto celebrate it.", 
            "dur": "4.35", 
            "start": "669.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then the last thing you\ndo is you shave your head.", 
            "dur": "3.67", 
            "start": "674.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the line for\nthe barber shop.", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "677.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is the line.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "680.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Soon, they will all be bald,\nall of these men.", 
            "dur": "3.065", 
            "start": "685.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The barber shops in Mecca\nhave these massive", 
            "dur": "2.455", 
            "start": "688.325"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lines outside of them.", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "690.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you see hundreds of\nthousands of baldos walking", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "692.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "around town.", 
            "dur": "0.81", 
            "start": "695.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And those people have\nall succeeded in", 
            "dur": "2.4", 
            "start": "696.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "completing their Hajj.", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "698.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they&#39;re called Hajjis.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "699.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Dealing with the Hajj every\nyear is a huge logistical", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "709.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "challenge for the Saudi\ngovernment--", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "711.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to the point where they&#39;ve\nactually set up", 
            "dur": "1.46", 
            "start": "713.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a Ministry of Hajj.", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "715"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In the past, there have been\nincidents where pilgrims were", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "716.97"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "trampled, when ramps collapsed\nand pilgrims died, and the", 
            "dur": "4.12", 
            "start": "719.19"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Saudi government has invested\nbillions of dollars to create", 
            "dur": "2.85", 
            "start": "723.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "an infrastructure to make this\nwork, with complex crowd", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "726.16"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "control techniques.", 
            "dur": "1.14", 
            "start": "729.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And what I saw when I went last\nyear was something that", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "730.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "somehow manages to work.", 
            "dur": "1.83", 
            "start": "733.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But it kind of goes without\nsaying that bringing 3 million", 
            "dur": "2.07", 
            "start": "740.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "people into such a small place\nis going to bring up some", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "742.32"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "complications.", 
            "dur": "1.71", 
            "start": "745.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s a bit of a dark side.", 
            "dur": "1.68", 
            "start": "746.82"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This many people in such\na small place,", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "748.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it really gets unwieldy.", 
            "dur": "1.39", 
            "start": "750.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And despite the Saudi\ngovernment&#39;s best efforts to", 
            "dur": "2.1", 
            "start": "752.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "deal with this profound\nlogistical challenge, the", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "754.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "bottom line is that there\nare too many people.", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "756.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And people need things.", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "758.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They need places to sleep.", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "761.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They need food.", 
            "dur": "0.806", 
            "start": "762.68"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The need toilets.", 
            "dur": "1.744", 
            "start": "763.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the poor people who were\nthere, you see them basically", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "765.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "camped out on the side of the\nroad for days on end.", 
            "dur": "3.24", 
            "start": "767.96"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It really felt like Mecca was\nmaxing out by the end of Hajj.", 
            "dur": "3.52", 
            "start": "771.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the whole scene starts\nlooking and feeling rather", 
            "dur": "2.549", 
            "start": "774.72"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "apocalyptic.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "777.269"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No matter where all these\npeople come from.", 
            "dur": "1.67", 
            "start": "812.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No matter what they do.", 
            "dur": "0.82", 
            "start": "813.91"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And no matter how rich or poor\nthey might be, during this", 
            "dur": "2.7", 
            "start": "814.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pilgrimage to Mecca it\nfelt like everyone", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "817.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "was just the same.", 
            "dur": "1.85", 
            "start": "819.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was unlike any place I&#39;ve\never been and unlike anything", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "821.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve ever experienced.", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "823.85"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was there standing amongst\nmillions of people, I was", 
            "dur": "3.21", 
            "start": "825.29"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there with my family, but, on\nsome level, I felt like I all", 
            "dur": "2.856", 
            "start": "828.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "alone, on a personal trek.", 
            "dur": "2.624", 
            "start": "831.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And everyday life felt like it\nwas hundreds of thousands of", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "833.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "miles away.", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "836.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We flew back to New York.", 
            "dur": "1.45", 
            "start": "838.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We landed in the morning, and\nI went straight back to the", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "839.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Vice offices, which\nmay not have been", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "841.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the wisests of ideas.", 
            "dur": "1.396", 
            "start": "843.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I felt like I&#39;d been catapulted\nfrom one end of the", 
            "dur": "2.314", 
            "start": "845.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "universe to the other.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "847.44"
        }
    ], 
